AppBarDataDefinitions.sqlFormat: UPDATE bar_element_summary a, (SELECT DATEDIFF(DATE(NOW()), IFNULL((DATE(p.created_date)),DATE(p.created_stamp))) AS lead_since,p.party_id FROM party p INNER JOIN party_role pr ON p.party_id=pr.party_id AND pr.role_type_id="LEAD" GROUP BY p.party_Id)b SET ELEMENT_VALUE_1 = b.lead_since WHERE a.party_id=b.Party_ID

UPDATE bar_element_summary a,(SELECT p.STATUS_ID AS status_id,P.party_id FROM PARTY P INNER JOIN PARTY_ROLE PR ON P.PARTY_ID=PR.PARTY_ID AND PR.ROLE_TYPE_ID="LEAD" GROUP BY p.party_id)b SET ELEMENT_VALUE_2 = b.status_id WHERE a.party_id=b.Party_ID

UPDATE bar_element_summary a,( SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT MC.`MARKETING_CAMPAIGN_ID` ) AS marketing_camp_id , CLP.party_id FROM MARKETING_CAMPAIGN MC INNER JOIN `marketing_campaign_contact_list` CL ON MC.MARKETING_CAMPAIGN_ID=CL.MARKETING_CAMPAIGN_ID INNER JOIN CONTACT_LIST_PARTY CLP ON CLP.CONTACT_LIST_ID=CL.CONTACT_LIST_ID INNER JOIN PARTY_ROLE PR ON PR.PARTY_ID=CLP.PARTY_ID WHERE MC.STATUS_ID IN ("MKTG_CAMP_CREATED","MKTG_CAMP_INPROGRESS","MKTG_CAMP_SCHEDULED") AND PR.ROLE_TYPE_ID="LEAD" GROUP BY CLP.PARTY_ID) b SET ELEMENT_VALUE_3 = b.marketing_camp_id WHERE a.party_id=b.Party_ID

UPDATE bar_element_summary a,(SELECT DATEDIFF(DATE(SO.ESTIMATED_CLOSE_DATE),DATE(NOW())) AS ESTIMATED_CLOSE_DATE, SO.PARTY_ID FROM SALES_OPPORTUNITY SO INNER JOIN `sales_opportunity_role` SOR ON SO.SALES_OPPORTUNITY_ID=SOR.SALES_OPPORTUNITY_ID AND SOR.ROLE_TYPE_ID="LEAD" GROUP BY SO.PARTY_ID) b SET ELEMENT_VALUE_4 = b.ESTIMATED_CLOSE_DATE WHERE a.party_id=b.party_id

UPDATE bar_element_summary a,(SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT S.SALES_OPPORTUNITY_ID) AS SALES_OPPORTUNITY_ID, SO.PARTY_ID FROM `sales_opportunity` S INNER JOIN SALES_OPPORTUNITY_ROLE SR ON S.SALES_OPPORTUNITY_ID=SR.SALES_OPPORTUNITY_ID AND S.OPPORTUNITY_STATUS_ID="OPPO_OPEN" AND SR.ROLE_TYPE_ID="LEAD" GROUP BY SO.PARTY_ID) b SET ELEMENT_VALUE_5 = b.SALES_OPPORTUNITY_ID WHERE a.party_id=b.party_id

UPDATE bar_element_summary a,(SELECT COUNT(*) AS cnt,we.party_id FROM work_effort w INNER JOIN work_Effort_party_assignment we ON w.work_effort_id=we.work_effort_id AND w.current_status_id="IA_OPEN" AND we.role_type_id="LEAD" GROUP BY we.party_id) b SET ELEMENT_VALUE_6 = b.cnt WHERE a.party_id=b.party_id

UPDATE bar_element_summary a,(SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT MC.`MARKETING_CAMPAIGN_ID` ) AS cnt,CLP.PARTY_ID FROM MARKETING_CAMPAIGN MC INNER JOIN `marketing_campaign_contact_list` CL ON MC.MARKETING_CAMPAIGN_ID=CL.MARKETING_CAMPAIGN_ID INNER JOIN CONTACT_LIST_PARTY CLP ON CLP.CONTACT_LIST_ID=CL.CONTACT_LIST_ID INNER JOIN PARTY_ROLE PR ON PR.PARTY_ID=CLP.PARTY_ID WHERE MC.STATUS_ID IN ("MKTG_CAMP_CREATED","MKTG_CAMP_INPROGRESS","MKTG_CAMP_SCHEDULED") AND PR.ROLE_TYPE_ID="LEAD" GROUP BY CLP.PARTY_ID) b SET ELEMENT_VALUE_7 = b.cnt WHERE a.party_id=b.party_id

UPDATE bar_element_summary a,(SELECT DATE(P.CALL_BACK_DATE) AS CALL_BACK_DATE,P.PARTY_ID FROM PERSON P INNER JOIN PARTY_ROLE PR ON P.PARTY_ID=PR.PARTY_ID AND PR.ROLE_TYPE_ID="LEAD" GROUP BY P.PARTY_ID) b SET ELEMENT_VALUE_8 = b.CALL_BACK_DATE WHERE a.party_id=b.party_id

UPDATE bar_element_summary a,(SELECT DATE(MC.`CLICK_DATE`) AS tmp,MC.PARTY_ID FROM MARKETING_CAMPAIGN_CLICKED_DETAILS MC INNER JOIN PARTY_ROLE PR ON MC.PARTY_ID=PR.PARTY_ID AND PR.ROLE_TYPE_ID="LEAD" GROUP BY MC.PARTY_ID) b SET ELEMENT_VALUE_9 = b.tmp WHERE a.party_id=b.party_id

UPDATE bar_element_summary a,(SELECT DATE(MC.`open_time`) AS tmp,MC.PARTY_ID FROM MARKETING_CAMPAIGN_OPEN_DETAILS MC INNER JOIN PARTY_ROLE PR ON MC.PARTY_ID=PR.PARTY_ROLE AND PR.ROLE_TYPE_ID="LEAD" GROUP BY PR.PARTY_ID) b SET ELEMENT_VALUE_10 = b.tmp WHERE a.party_id=b.party_id

UPDATE bar_element_summary a,(SELECT DATEDIFF(DATE(NOW()),DATE(a.CREATED_DATE)) AS days,b.party_id FROM work_Effort a INNER JOIN work_effort_party_assignment b ON a.work_effort_id=b.work_Effort_id INNER JOIN party_relationship c ON b.party_id=c.party_id_TO AND c.party_relationship_type_id="CONTACT_REL_INV" AND role_type_id="LEAD" GROUP BY b.party_id) d SET ELEMENT_VALUE_11 = d.days WHERE a.party_id=d.party_id

UPDATE bar_element_summary a,(SELECT DATE(MC.`CLICK_DATE`) AS tmp,MC.PARTY_ID FROM MARKETING_CAMPAIGN_CLICKED_DETAILS MC INNER JOIN PARTY_ROLE PR ON MC.PARTY_ID=PR.PARTY_ID AND PR.ROLE_TYPE_ID="LEAD" GROUP BY MC.PARTY_ID) b SET ELEMENT_VALUE_12 = b.tmp WHERE a.party_id=b.party_id
